parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the automatic seat belt can cause the belt to malfunction, leading to inadequate restraint in the event of an accident, which can increase the risk of injury or fatality.
symptoms: The seat belt tightens too much and over-retracts
the seat belt retracts too tightly and chokes the occupants
the motor belt part of the seat belt fails.
